      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented SQA plans with version control, regression testing, and change management procedures consistent with Gradation 3 requirements."
