      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V, cobalt-chrome rod) sourced from certified coupon test data supplied by DePuy Synthes. Geometry derived from CAD files. Uncertainty in input parameters quantified and propagated through ensemble runs."
