      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "N=11 production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Sample dimensions and surface finish verified against device master record prior to testing."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
