      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load level and displacement rate per ASTM F1717. Variation in test conditions (e.g., load magnitude, rate, temperature) was not explored, limiting the factor to Gradation 2. This deficiency is noted as an acceptable risk given the deterministic nature of the static compression-bending scenario."
    },
