      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities replicate the F1717 test configuration directly. Construct geometry, material, and loading mode match those of the regulatory submission scenario, supporting direct relevance of the validation evidence."
